data.description: 64 Healey Ct is welcoming you home with solar power to keep you energy efficient!  The only Double driveway on the row as you approach the front of the home, giving you ample parking for 4 cars total depending on size. 1 car garage is a bonus space for more parking or storage but has most recently had additional insulation added and used as a movie room.  electric car? No problem! Already a plug ready for you to charge. Spacious 2 story townhome greets you as you open the front door to LVP flooring on the entire main level and a convenient coat closet as you come inside.  Open concept Living/ Dining/ Kitchen concept with gorgeous granite counters and the highly sought after dark kitchen cabinets accented with Stainless steel appliances. Oversize bedrooms and a primary suite that offers a stand up shower with seat, private water closet, dual sinks, and a walk-in closet. Upper story laundry for a breezy laundry day! No lugging up and down the stairs. Fenced backyard with hot tub conveying! Transform this space into your backyard oasis.
